title: ArcGIS Portal Index Sync
agents: special
catalog: app/arcgis
license: MIT
distribution: custom

description:
 This check monitors the overall Portal index synchronization status.

 It is separate from the per-index count checks. The per-index checks compare
 individual database and index counts, while this check reports the overall sync
 status returned by Portal.
item:
 This check has no item.
discovery:
 One service is discovered when Portal reports an index sync status.
